---
import Section from './Section.astro';
---

<Section id="about" eyebrow="About" heading="Defense at scale, learning in public">
  <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-5 text-muted-fg">
    <p>
      I'm a Senior Security Analyst at
      <a
        href="https://www.criticalstart.com"
        rel="noopener"
        class="text-foreground underline decoration-line underline-offset-4 transition-colors duration-(--duration-fast) hover:text-accent hover:decoration-accent"
      >Critical Start</a>, working across multiple SIEM and EDR/XDR platforms to
      triage, investigate, contain, and escalate threats in 2,500+ multi-tenant
      customer environments. My focus is threat investigation, log analysis, and
      tuning detection logic to cut alert noise at scale.
    </p>
    <p>
      Alongside analyst work, I build security-focused projects to learn the
      underlying technologies hands-on and automate routine SOC tasks. Right now
      I'm going deeper on detection engineering: writing and testing my own
      detection rules, and documenting what I learn on the
      <a
        href="/blog"
        class="text-foreground underline decoration-line underline-offset-4 transition-colors duration-(--duration-fast) hover:text-accent hover:decoration-accent"
      >blog</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Section>
